---
// colorfix_for_all_lp.html のデザインをベースに、PDF解析アプリ向けに調整したランディングページ
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ColorFix for All — 色をなおす、デザインを守る</title>
  <meta name="description" content="PDFをドラッグ＆ドロップするだけ。色覚多様性とロービジョンに配慮した改善色を、元デザインの印象をできるだけ保ちながら提案します。" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #1A5C3A;
      --primary-btn: #145530;
      --primary-light: #52B788;
      --primary-pale: #D8F3DC;
      --accent: #D4A017;
      --text: #1B2A22;
      --text-secondary: #3D5449;
      --bg: #FAFFFE;
      --bg-alt: #EFF8F2;
      --surface: #FFFFFF;
      --border: #B8DEC8;
      --radius: 12px;
      --shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(26,92,58,0.10);
      --shadow-lg: 0 8px 40px rgba(26,92,58,0.16);
      --max-w: 1080px;
      --font: "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN", "Hiragino Sans", Meiryo, sans-serif;
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: var(--font); color: var(--text); background: var(--bg); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 16px; }
    a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: underline; }
    a:hover { color: var(--primary-light); }
    .container { max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(250,255,254,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 0 24px;
    }
    .nav-inner {
      max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; height: 60px;
    }
    .nav-logo { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
    .nav-logo .logo-icon { width: 30px; height: 30px; background: var(--primary); border-radius: 7px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 15px; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; transition: color .15s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--primary); }
    .nav-cta { background: var(--primary-btn); color: #FFF; border: none; padding: 9px 22px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; transition: background .15s; display: inline-block; }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: #0F3D28; color: #FFF; }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(140deg, #0D3522 0%, #1A8A52 100%);
      color: #FFF;
      padding: 88px 0 80px;
    }
    .hero-inner {
      max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: center;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      background: rgba(82,183,136,0.22); border: 1px solid rgba(82,183,136,0.45);
      padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px; color: #A8E0C0;
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.18; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 18px; color: #FFF; }
    .hero h1 .em { color: #F0C040; }
    .hero-desc { font-size: 1.02rem; color: #C8EAD8; margin-bottom: 32px; max-width: 440px; line-height: 1.75; }
    .hero-desc strong { color: #FFF; }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 7px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; border: none; transition: transform .15s, box-shadow .15s, background .15s; }
    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.22); }
    .btn-primary { background: #E8B020; color: #1A2010; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #F0C040; color: #1A2010; }
    .btn-secondary { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.40); color: #FFF; }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.20); color: #FFF; }

    /* HERO DEMO */
    .demo-compare-wrap {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.20);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px;
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px;
    }
    .demo-col { flex: 1; min-width: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
    .demo-col-label {
      font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .08em; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;
    }
    .bad-label { background: #D32F2F; color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 0.72rem; padding: 4px 10px; }
    .good-label { background: #1A5C3A; color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 0.72rem; padding: 4px 10px; border: 1px solid #52B788; }
    .demo-page {
      background: #FFFFFF;
      border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;
      border: 2px solid rgba(180,50,30,0.55);
      padding: 12px 14px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 7px;
    }
    .demo-page.good { border-color: rgba(40,160,80,0.60); }
    .demo-page-topbar { height: 4px; border-radius: 2px; }
    .demo-page-heading { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.3; font-family: sans-serif; }
    .demo-page-body { font-size: 0.72rem; line-height: 1.5; font-family: sans-serif; }
    .demo-page-btn {
      font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px; color: #FFF; display: inline-block; align-self: flex-start;
      font-family: sans-serif;
    }
    .demo-meta-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 2px; }
    .demo-dot { width: 14px; height: 14px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
    .demo-code { font-size: 0.76rem; font-family: monospace; color: #E8F4EE; font-weight: 700; }
    .demo-badge { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 800; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 4px; }
    .badge-fail { background: #B71C1C; color: #FFFFFF; }
    .badge-pass { background: #1A5C3A; color: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid #52B788; }
    .demo-verdict { font-size: 0.72rem; line-height: 1.4; }
    .bad-verdict { color: #FFCDD2; font-weight: 700; }
    .good-verdict { color: #C8E6C9; font-weight: 700; }

    .demo-arrow-col {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
      justify-content: center; gap: 4px; flex-shrink: 0;
      padding: 0 2px; margin-top: 52px;
    }
    .demo-arrow-icon { font-size: 1.3rem; color: #F0C040; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; }
    .demo-arrow-note { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4); padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 6px; }

    /* SECTIONS */
    .section-white { background: var(--bg); padding: 80px 0; }
    .section-alt { background: var(--bg-alt); padding: 80px 0; }
    .section-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .1em; color: var(--primary); background: var(--primary-pale); padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    h2 { font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.1rem); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.25; margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--text); }
    .section-lead { font-size: 1.02rem; color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 48px; line-height: 1.75; }

    /* CARDS */
    .problem-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .problem-item { background: var(--surface); border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 28px 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
    .problem-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .problem-item h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text); }
    .problem-item p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.65; }

    /* DIFF TABLE */
    .diff-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 40px; background: var(--surface); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
    .diff-table th { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 800; padding: 14px 20px; text-align: left; background: #0D3522; color: #FFF; }
    .diff-table td { padding: 14px 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text); }
    .diff-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .diff-table tr:hover td { background: var(--bg-alt); }
    .feature-name { font-weight: 700; }
    .check { color: #1A6B38; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .cross { color: #B03020; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; }

    /* STEPS */
    .steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; margin-top: 48px; }
    .step { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 72px 1fr; align-items: stretch; }
    .step-left { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
    .step-num { width: 48px; height: 48px; background: var(--primary); color: #FFF; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .step-line { width: 2px; flex: 1; background: var(--border); margin: 4px 0; }
    .step:last-child .step-line { display: none; }
    .step-body { padding: 0 0 40px 20px; }
    .step-body h3 { font-size: 1.08rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--text); }
    .step-body p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }

    /* FEATURES */
    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; margin-top: 48px; }
    .feature-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 28px 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); transition: box-shadow .2s, transform .2s; }
    .feature-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .feature-card .icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 14px; display: inline-block; background: var(--primary-pale); padding: 10px; border-radius: 10px; }
    .feature-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--text); }
    .feature-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.65; }

    /* STANDARD */
    .standard-box { background: var(--surface); border: 1.5px solid #8CC8A8; border-left: 5px solid var(--primary); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 28px 32px; margin-top: 40px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .standard-item h4 { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 5px; }
    .standard-item p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.65; }
    .standard-note { grid-column: 1 / -1; font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-secondary); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 16px; }

    /* FAQ */
    .faq-list { margin-top: 44px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    details { background: var(--surface); border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; }
    details[open] { border-color: #52B788; }
    summary { padding: 18px 24px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.98rem; cursor: pointer; list-style: none; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; color: var(--text); }
    summary::after { content: "+"; font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--primary); flex-shrink: 0; transition: transform .2s; }
    details[open] summary::after { transform: rotate(45deg); }
    .faq-body { padding: 0 24px 20px; font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.75; }

    /* CTA BOTTOM */
    .cta-section { background: #0D3522; color: #FFF; text-align: center; padding: 100px 24px; }
    .cta-section h2 { color: #FFF; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { color: #C8E8D8; margin-bottom: 36px; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75; }
    .cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-cta-primary { background: #E8B020; color: #1A2010; }
    .btn-cta-primary:hover { background: #F0C040; color: #1A2010; }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer { background: #081A0E; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.70); padding: 40px 24px; }
    .footer-inner { max-width: var(--max-w); margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; }
    .footer-logo { font-weight: 900; color: #90C8A8; font-size: 1rem; }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
      .hero-visual { display: none; }
      .problem-grid, .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .standard-box { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="#" class="nav-logo">
      <span class="logo-icon">&#x1F3A8;</span>
      ColorFix for All
    </a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#how">使い方</a></li>
      <li><a href="#features">機能</a></li>
      <li><a href="#standard">規格</a></li>
      <li><a href="#faq">FAQ</a></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="/app" class="nav-cta">PDFで試す &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="hero-badge">&#x1F52C; ISO 24505-2:2025 準拠設計</div>
      <h1>色をなおす、<br><span class="em">デザインを守る。</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        PDFをブラウザにドロップするだけ。色覚多様性とロービジョンに配慮した<strong>改善色</strong>を、元デザインの印象をできるだけ保ちながら提案します。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/app" class="btn btn-primary">PDFで試す &rarr;</a>
        <a href="#how" class="btn btn-secondary">どう動く？</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Before/After デモ：実際の文字の見え方を左右で比較 -->
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="demo-compare-wrap">

        <!-- BEFORE -->
        <div class="demo-col">
          <span class="demo-col-label bad-label">&#9888; BEFORE — 修正前</span>
          <div class="demo-page">
            <div class="demo-page-topbar" style="background:#4CAF50"></div>
            <p class="demo-page-heading" style="color:#4CAF50">資料のテキスト</p>
            <p class="demo-page-body" style="color:#4CAF50">PDF配布資料の文字色。白背景では読みにくい。</p>
            <span class="demo-page-btn" style="background:#4CAF50">ボタン</span>
          </div>
          <div class="demo-meta-row">
            <span class="demo-dot" style="background:#4CAF50"></span>
            <code class="demo-code">#4CAF50</code>
            <span class="demo-badge badge-fail">2.1:1 &#x2717;</span>
          </div>
          <p class="demo-verdict bad-verdict">白背景では読みにくい</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 変換の矢印と説明 -->
        <div class="demo-arrow-col">
          <div class="demo-arrow-icon">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="demo-arrow-note">明度を下げて<br>緑を維持</div>
        </div>

        <!-- AFTER -->
        <div class="demo-col">
          <span class="demo-col-label good-label">&#10003; AFTER — 修正後</span>
          <div class="demo-page good">
            <div class="demo-page-topbar" style="background:#1B6B35"></div>
            <p class="demo-page-heading" style="color:#1B6B35">資料のテキスト</p>
            <p class="demo-page-body" style="color:#1B6B35">同じ緑系でも、暗くすれば読みやすくなる。</p>
            <span class="demo-page-btn" style="background:#1B6B35">ボタン</span>
          </div>
          <div class="demo-meta-row">
            <span class="demo-dot" style="background:#1B6B35"></span>
            <code class="demo-code">#1B6B35</code>
            <span class="demo-badge badge-pass">5.8:1 &#10003; AA</span>
          </div>
          <p class="demo-verdict good-verdict">緑の印象を保ちつつ読みやすく</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PROBLEM -->
<div class="section-alt" id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-tag">課題</span>
    <h2>既存のPDFアクセシビリティツールは<br>「直せない」</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">シミュレーターは「見え方」を教えてくれますが、現場で必要なのは「具体的な改善値」です。</p>
    <div class="problem-grid">
      <div class="problem-item"><div class="problem-icon">&#x1F441;&#xFE0F;</div><h3>シミュレーションだけで終わる</h3><p>「こう見える」は分かっても「どう直せばよいか」を返してくれるツールはほとんどありません。</p></div>
      <div class="problem-item"><div class="problem-icon">&#x274C;</div><h3>AIによる不安定な推論</h3><p>AIやVLMに頼ると、毎回違う色を提案されたり、元のデザイン意図を無視した色が返されることがあります。</p></div>
      <div class="problem-item"><div class="problem-icon">&#x1F3A8;</div><h3>ブランドが壊れる</h3><p>ただコントラストを上げようと黒や白に寄せてしまうと、ブランドの「色相」が失われてしまいます。</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- DIFF TABLE -->
<div class="section-white">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-tag">違い</span>
    <h2>ColorFix for All がやること</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">PDF上のコントラスト判定の先、具体的な色数値まで踏み込みます。</p>
    <table class="diff-table">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>機能</th><th>シミュレーター</th><th>一般的なAIツール</th><th>ColorFix for All</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td class="feature-name">色覚多様性の見え方確認</td><td><span class="check">&#10004;</span></td><td><span class="partial">&#9651; 不確定</span></td><td><span class="check">&#10004; 数理ベース</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td class="feature-name">機密PDFのローカル処理</td><td><span class="cross">&#10007;</span></td><td><span class="cross">&#10007; サーバー送信</span></td><td><span class="check">&#10004; ブラウザ完結</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td class="feature-name">具体的な改善色の提案</td><td><span class="cross">&#10007;</span></td><td><span class="partial">&#9651; コロコロ変わる</span></td><td><span class="check">&#10004; Delta E最小化</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td class="feature-name">元の色相を保つ補正</td><td><span class="cross">&#10007;</span></td><td><span class="cross">&#10007;</span></td><td><span class="check">&#10004;</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td class="feature-name">ISO 24505-2:2025 準拠設計</td><td><span class="cross">&#10007;</span></td><td><span class="cross">&#10007;</span></td><td><span class="check">&#10004;</span></td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- HOW -->
<div class="section-alt" id="how">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-tag">使い方</span>
    <h2>3ステップでPDFを改善</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">サーバーへのアップロード不要。機密の社内資料もブラウザ内で安全に解析します。</p>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step"><div class="step-left"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-line"></div></div><div class="step-body"><h3>PDFをドロップ</h3><p>分析したいPDFファイルを画面にドラッグ＆ドロップします。</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-left"><div class="step-num">2</div><div class="step-line"></div></div><div class="step-body"><h3>自動解析</h3><p>ブラウザ上で直接テキストと背景色を描画・サンプリングし、見えづらい箇所をハイライトします。</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-left"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-line"></div></div><div class="step-body"><h3>改善候補を受け取る</h3><p>色味（Hue）を保ったまま、明度と彩度を数学的に調整した「正しい色」をワンクリックでコピーできます。</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<div class="section-white" id="features">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-tag">機能</span>
    <h2>主要機能</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card"><span class="icon">&#x1F50D;</span><h3>文字の可読性ファースト</h3><p>不要な装飾や背景画像への過剰な指摘を排除し、テキスト文字のコントラスト評価にフォーカスします。</p></div>
